rating_comment: I loved the place and the overall support of the host throughout my stay. Indeed, a value for what you have paid for. In one words, I simply felt at home. However, the place may not be suitable for those who are late night comers.

info: Rating, 5 stars,  · April 2024,  · Stayed about a week
rating_comment:
Amazing room. The best option for your money. The house is very quiet, tidy and safe. Lubaba accepted me in the best traditions, she made sure that I didn’t need anything. She constantly found out if I needed anything. And she always answered instantly. It was very comfortable, as if I had come home to stay with my parents. Thanks for the wonderful experience!
Location 10/10, you can buy everything you need just a few steps away.
